<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="preparation-n">preparation <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌprepə'reɪʃn/    美 /ˌprepə'reɪʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>准备；预备：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I did adequate <strong>preparation for</strong> the examination.
我为考试作了充足的准备。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>准备工作：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All the <strong>preparations for</strong> the task have been completed, and we’re ready to start. 
这项任务的所有准备工作都已经完成，我们可以开始了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-preparation-for">in preparation for</h3>
<p>1.<strong>为…作准备：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I want to improve my language skills in preparation for further study overseas. 
我想提高我的语言技能为出国深造作准备。</p></div>

<h3 id="make-preparations-for">make preparations for</h3>
<p>1.<strong>为…作准备：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They are busy making preparations for the wedding.
他们正忙着筹备婚礼。</p></div></div>